divs: Sighting DetailsMyself and 3 friends were having a smoke on the balcony of my apartment, and observed a redish orange light moving from what seemed to be above the hone bridge, to the left, and we watched the object for 3 minutes move across the sky, randomly becoming darker and lighter.
Summary: redish orange light, moving with precision horizontally across sky
